~OLCommand :~RS call
~OLUsage   :~RS call [<user>]
~OLAliases :~RS ,

Allows you to set up a quick way of telling a user a message. If you
omit the user then you will be shown which user you have currently set
to quick call.

Quick call is used such as: ,hi there, how are ya?

Which will send the "hi there, how are ya?" to whomever is set in the
quick call.
